FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [l].[Id], [l].[Category], [l].[Code], [l].[CreatedAt], [l].[DetectionPatternsJson], [l].[DisplayName], [l].[HasPerformanceMetrics], [l].[Icon], [l].[IsActive], [l].[ShowInDashboard], [l].[SortOrder], [l].[UpdatedAt], [l].[UpdatedBy]
    FROM [LMResourceTypes] AS [l]
    WHERE [l].[Code] = @__typeCode_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [l0].[Id], [l0].[CreatedAt], [l0].[CriticalThreshold], [l0].[DatapointPatternsJson], [l0].[DatasourcePatternsJson], [l0].[DisplayName], [l0].[InvertThreshold], [l0].[IsActive], [l0].[MetricName], [l0].[OversizedBelow], [l0].[ResourceTypeId], [l0].[SortOrder], [l0].[UndersizedAbove], [l0].[Unit], [l0].[UpdatedAt], [l0].[WarningThreshold]
    FROM [LMMetricMappings] AS [l0]
    WHERE [l0].[IsActive] = CAST(1 AS bit)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ResourceTypeId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id]
